OL,3,CVictoria Square residents win bid to
OL,4,Csecure rehearing in compensation case
OL,6,FResidents evacuated from a Belfast
OL,7,Fapartment block due to safety concerns
OL,8,Fhave won a legal battle to secure a
OL,9,Frehearing in their multi-million pound
OL,10,Fbid for compensation.
OL,12,FLawsuits brought over alleged flaws in
OL,13,Fthe Victoria Square complex were
OL,14,Foriginally dismissed by a judge for
OL,15,Fbeing out of time.
OL,17,FBut it was conceded in the Court of
OL,18,FAppeal today that the claims based on
OL,19,Fdefective premises legislation were
OL,20,Fnever finally determined.
