OL,6,FBarrister Anna Rowan, appearing for
OL,7,Fsome of the apartment owners,
OL,8,Fconfirmed: "That aspect is returning
OL,9,Fto the judge for a full trial on the
OL,10,Fmerits."
OL,12,FThe outcome is being seen as a victory
OL,13,Fin attempts to pursue the case using
OL,14,Fnew laws which widens the scope for
OL,15,Flitigation in Northern Ireland.
OL,17,FCompleted back in 2008, the Victoria
OL,18,FSquare residential development on
OL,19,FChichester Street has been empty for
OL,20,Fthe past five years.
