OL,3,CVictoria Square residents win bid to
OL,4,Csecure rehearing in compensation case
OL,6,FIn April 2019, residents in all 91
OL,7,Fapartments were told to move out
OL,8,Ffollowing assessments of a structural
OL,9,Fcolumn.
OL,11,FUlster Garden Villages Ltd, a charity
OL,12,Fwhich owns more than half the flats,
OL,13,Fand individual owners joined forces to
OL,14,Fsue the builders and architects
OL,15,Finvolved in the city centre
OL,16,Fdevelopment.
OL,18,FThey claimed for structural defects,
OL,19,Fnegligence and loss of value in joint
OL,20,Flawsuits estimated to be worth up to
OL,21,F#25m.
