OL,6,FConstruction firms Farrans and Gilbert-
OL,7,FAsh, along with architecture company
OL,8,FBuilding Design Partnership,
OL,9,Fvehemently denied any liability.
OL,11,FIn March, the three defendants
OL,12,Fsuccessfully applied to have the
OL,13,Factions struck out at the High Court
OL,14,Fon the grounds that it was statute
OL,15,Fbarred.
