OL,3,CVictoria Square residents win bid to
OL,4,Csecure rehearing in compensation case
OL,6,FUnder laws in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fcompensation claims for defective
OL,8,Fpremises must be lodged within six
OL,9,Fyears of a building being completed -
OL,10,Funlike the 30 year timeframe in
OL,11,FEngland and Wales.
OL,13,FMr Justice Huddleston dismissed the
OL,14,Factions after finding that the
OL,15,Fapartment owners were caught by that
OL,16,Flimit.
OL,18,FA challenge to that ruling was mounted
OL,19,Fat the Court of Appeal.
