OL,3,CVictoria Square residents win bid to
OL,4,Csecure rehearing in compensation case
OL,6,FMeanwhile, amid widespread public
OL,7,Fsympathy for those who have lost their
OL,8,Fhomes, Communities Minister Gordon
OL,9,FLyons moved to introduce new laws to
OL,10,Fbring Northern Ireland into line with
OL,11,Fthe rest of the UK.
OL,13,FThe Defective Premises Act (NI) 2024
OL,14,Fhas now received royal assent and come
OL,15,Finto effect.
OL,17,FLawyers representing Ulster Garden
OL,18,FVillages and some of the other owners
OL,19,Fargued that the claims should be
OL,20,Freconsidered due to the change in the
OL,21,Flegislative landscape.
