OL,3,CVictoria Square residents win bid to
OL,4,Csecure rehearing in compensation case
OL,6,FIn court today, appeal judges agreed
OL,7,Fto make an order for the claims to be
OL,8,Fsent back for further determination.
OL,10,FCommending both sides on the
OL,11,Fresolution, Lady Chief Justice Dame
OL,12,FSiobhan Keegan said: "This has been a
OL,13,Flong-running case, we hope that the
OL,14,Ffirst instance proceedings can be
OL,15,Ftaken up again as swiftly as possible."
OL,17,FShe also asked if any potential
OL,18,Fmediation or arbitration process had
OL,19,Fbeen explored.
